video.title: Pocoyo
video.synopsis: Discovery is the name of the game for friendly toddler Pocoyo in this lifelike and richly colored animated adventure series for preschoolers.

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and his pals celebrate the holidays and show each other their new toys. Pocoyo, Pato and Elly play a fun game with marbles.
episodes.title: Holidays / Christmas Tree / Hole Lotta Trouble / Chicks Dig Me

episodes.synopsis: Pato is really into his new phone! The Angry Alien returns and impersonates Pocoyo. The three friends work to help the environment.
episodes.title: Call Me / Angry Alien Strikes Back / Muck Struck / Nina

episodes.synopsis: Elly loves soccer! Later, Pocoyo and friends meet Nina, a small girl who lives in the plants with her robot, Roberto. It's time to pick berries!
episodes.title: Hack Attack / House of Colors / Disco Fleaver / Bumbleberry Surprise

episodes.synopsis: While Pocoyo and Nina play, Elly continues to cook delicious cakes. A group of green Martians visit and take photos of the friends.
episodes.title: Great Shot! / Time After Time Before Time / Magic Words / Tourist Trapped

episodes.synopsis: Sleepy Bird wants a nice nap, but Pocoyo keeps banging on his drum! Pocoyo and his friends start a rock band. It's also Nina's first Halloween.
episodes.title: Dance Off Part Two / Sleep Guard / Summer Hike / Rock Is a Hard Place / Halloween Tales

episodes.synopsis: Pato the postman is making his rounds and has to deliver a package to a green Martian. Elly wants to soak up some sun at the beach.
episodes.title: Tiny Fun Park / Space Postal Service / An Alien Christmas Carol / Are We There Yet? / Insert Coin

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo learns about instruments and starts a band. The trio of friends goes on a picnic. Pato gets ready for a shower. Pocoyo visits Pato's garden.
episodes.title: Pocoyo's Band / Picnic / Pato's Shower / The Garden

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo needs a postman to deliver a letter. Pocoyo builds a colorful tower. The friends challenge each other to a race. Everyone goes camping.
episodes.title: Pato the  Postman / Colours / Ready, Steady, Go / Camping

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and Pato play with their Martian friend. Pato is about to take a trip on a plane, but forgets his suitcase. The friends play tennis.
episodes.title: Space Mission / Travel with Pato /  Playtime / Tennis Everyone

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo learns how to play hide-and-seek. With cake and balloons, everyone gets ready for a party! The friends go for a fun ride.
episodes.title: Hide and Seek / Party Time / Wheels / Elly's Bath

episodes.synopsis: Pato stacks colorful blocks into a tower. Loula gets filthy in the mud, so Pocoyo and Elly give her a bath. Pocoyo uses his wand for magic tricks.
episodes.title: The Amazing Tower / Pocoyo's New Toys / Bathing Loula / Magic Fingers

episodes.synopsis: Elly bakes a yummy cake for Caterpillar. The friends play at Elly's market. Pato sings a lullaby before bed. Elly and Pocoyo play golf.
episodes.title: Cooking with Elly / Elly's Market / Pato's Bedtime /  A Hole in One

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo finds a camera and takes pictures of his friends. The friends paint a still life. Pocoyo shows off a trick with his magic boxes.
episodes.title: Pocoyo's Camera / Painting with Pocoyo / Playing Dress Up / Magic Box

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and Elly set up a restaurant. The friends pretend to be pirates in search of treasure. Elly enjoys playing games on the computer.
episodes.title: Pocoyo's Restaurant / Wake Up, Pocoyo! / Ahoy, Pocoyo! / Elly's Computer

episodes.synopsis: The postman delivers a postcard from Elly, who is at the beach. Pocoyo plays with a remote control. Pocoyo learns about things in a supermarket.
episodes.title: Going To The Beach / Big and Small / Face Painting / Pocoyo's Supermarket

episodes.synopsis: Elly squeezes into a little playhouse. Pocoyo builds a theater for puppets and stages a show. The friends learn from a group of colorful aliens.
episodes.title: Elly's Playhouse / Pocoyo's Puppet Theatre / Up and Down / Pocoyo's Breakfast

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo loves pretending he is a traffic cop. Pato arranges his living room and hosts his friends. Elly's doll needs a babysitter.
episodes.title: Traffic Jam / Pato's Living Room / Cinema / Elly's New Doll

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo, Elly and Pato set up a colorful circus. The friends discuss who has the best bedroom. Pocoyo and his friends get geared up for school.
episodes.title: Circus / The Best Bedroom / Pocoyo Goes to School / Art

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and Pato learn about recycling. In the garden, the friends plant colorful veggies. To avoid cleaning up, Pocoyo pretends to have a cold.
episodes.title: Pocoyo Recycles / Down on the Farm / Nurse Elly / Fishing with Pocoyo

episodes.synopsis: Pato doesn't want to join in the games with his friends. / Pocoyo plays a game involving strange shapes. / Pocoyo wants to play but everyone is gone.
episodes.title: Mr. Big Duck / Guess What? / All for One / Band of Friends

episodes.synopsis: Pato gets stuck hanging upside down. / Pocoyo finds a super machine that mixes objects. / Pocoyo makes a mess and leaves it for friends to clean up.
episodes.title: Upside Down / Mad Mix Machine / The Messy Guest / New on the Planet

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo has a beautifully wrapped up present but he won't open it. / Elly wants to be a prima ballerina. / Pocoyo accidentally lets go of a balloon.
episodes.title: Pocoyo's Present / Elly's Ballet Class / Pocoyo's Balloon / Who's Calling Me Now?

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo is too scared of a new slide. / Elly gets a fancy new pair of dress shoes. / Pocoyo finds a strange door that leads to the sky.
episodes.title: Big Scary Slide / Elly's Shoes / Duck Stuck / Scary Noises

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo finds old rubbish and decides to clear it out. / Pocoyo promises to teach Baby Bird to drive the Vamoosh. / Elly's darling doll is missing.
episodes.title: Not in My Backyard / Vamoosh on the Loosh / Detective Pocoyo / Scooter Madness

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo goes to visit his alien friend. / Pocoyo makes a new game called BOO! / Pocoyo is having a party and invites all his friends.
episodes.title: Lost in Space / Boo! / Party Pooper / My Pato

episodes.synopsis: Baby Bird is in awe of Pocoyo as he plays skillfully with a bouncy ball. / Pato thinks Loula stinks. / Pocoyo finds a seed and plants it.
episodes.title: Baby Bird Bother / Dirty Dog / The Seed / Runaway Hat

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo finds a machine that makes things invisible. / Pocoyo, Elly and Baby Bird make a lot of noise. / Sleepy Bird needs someone to watch Baby Bird.
episodes.title: Invisible Pocoyo / Noise to My Ears / Baby Bird Sitting / Everyone's Present

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo is doing a magic show. / Pocoyo and Elly organize a picnic. / Pocoyo makes a puppet show. / Pato finds an egg and falls in love with it.
episodes.title: Magic Act / Picnic Puzzle / Pocoyo's Puppet Show / Pato's Egg

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and Pato stumble upon a disco and Elly is the DJ. / Everyone plays hide and seek. / Pato, Pocoyo and Elly are having fun running and jumping.
episodes.title: Dance Off! / Get Lost Loula / Sneaky Shoes / Shutterbug

episodes.synopsis: An angry alien declares that he wants to be king. / Pato plays underwater with Octopus and Whale. / Everyone's preparing for a painting exhibition.
episodes.title: Angry Alien / Pato Underwater / Pato's Paintings / Monster Mystery

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and Pato pretend to be monsters; Pocoyo and Pato ice skate; Pato is leaving; Pocoyo wants to play ball but Pato wants to play on the see-saw.
episodes.title: Poczilla / Elly on Ice / Farewell Friends / Double Trouble

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo sees a horse! / Elly hosts a tea party, but no one wants to go. / The gang has a talent show. / Pocoyo shows his pals his favorite memories.
episodes.title: Horse! / Elly's Tea Party / Talent Show / Remember When

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo finds an umbrella. / Pocoyo and his playmates love dancing to the Ball Orchestra's music. / Pocoyo shows us that tidying can be fun.
episodes.title: Umbrella, Umbrella / Drum Roll Please / Swept Away / Who's on the Phone?

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and Loula are going to the beach, but have lost their ball. / Pocoyo has an unusual new friend. / Pocoyo makes a special present for Elly.
episodes.title: Fetch Loula Fetch! / A Little Cloud / A Present for Elly / Pocoyo Dance

episodes.synopsis: Elly has a cold and is sneezing too big. / Pocoyo has to figure out who has a camera. / Pocoyo and his gang want to make friends with a butterfly.
episodes.title: The Big Sneeze / A Mystery Most Puzzling / Hush / Double Bubble

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo finds a key which leads him on a magical adventure. / Pato and Elly enjoy a skipping rope. / Sleepy Bird's egg takes on a life of its own.
episodes.title: The Key to It All / Keep Going, Pocoyo! / Sleepy Bird's Surprise / Where's Pocoyo?

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo wants to drum, but his friends are all busy. / Elly and Pocoyo have a race. / Pocoyo is left in charge of guarding the castle Elly built.
episodes.title: Drummer Boy / The Great Race / Don't Touch! / Mystery Footprints

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo gives the last drop from his watering can to his friends. / Pocoyo and Elly play restaurants. / Elly finds a star that fell from the night sky.
episodes.title: Magical Watering / Table for Fun / Twinkle Twinkle / Hiccup

episodes.synopsis: When Pocoyo sends a letter to Elly, Pato is the postman. / Pocoyo neglects Loula when he finds a toy dog. / It's time to play baseball with Octopus.
episodes.title: Pato's Postal Service / Puppy Love / Bat and Ball / Elly Spots

episodes.synopsis: A model airplane shoots off into space. / Pocoyo's friends give him a surprise party. / Pocoyo and Pato have a ball that takes on a life of its own.
episodes.title: Up Up and Away / A Surprise for Pocoyo / Having a Ball / Super Pocoyo

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and Pato have too much luggage for their camping trip. / Pocoyo discovers his echo. / Elly inadvertently sets off on a fantastic journey.
episodes.title: Let's Go Camping! / Pocoyo, Pocoyo / Elly's Big Chase / Pocoyo Gets It Right

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo is impressed with Octopus's juggling. / Pato, fresh from a shower, tries to keep clean. / Pocoyo pretends to be an elephant, a duck and a dog.
episodes.title: Juggling Balls / Fussy Duck / A Dog's Life / Pocoyolympics

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo imagines that fish live in different places and draws funny pictures. / It's Whale's birthday. / Pocoyo befriends a hungry caterpillar.
episodes.title: Picture This / Whale's Birthday / Pocoyo's Little Friend / Colour My World

episodes.synopsis: It's Pocoyo and Pato's bedtime but Pocoyo isn't tired. / Pocoyo and Pato build a wall between themselves. / Octopus tries to get Pato to giggle.
episodes.title: Bedtime / A Little Something Between Friends / Giggle Bug / What's in the Box?

episodes.synopsis: Pocoyo and Pato have great fun playing with some magical blocks. / Pocoyo has decided to paint a portrait. / Pocoyo looks after Elly's favorite doll.
episodes.title: Musical Blocks / Paint Me a Picture! / Elly's Doll / Wackily Ever After
